de.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts97" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts104" ANNOTATION_ID="a2129592"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wenn/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts104" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts116" ANNOTATION_ID="a2129640"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie hat schöne Dinge in ihrem Leben getan.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts116" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts142" ANNOTATION_ID="a2675105"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie war ein gutes Vorbild für mich.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts193" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts217" ANNOTATION_ID="a2129787"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, meine Mutter hat viel von ihr erzählt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts217" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts230" ANNOTATION_ID="a3371533"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Und von ihrem Unfall, so wusste ich viel über sie.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts230" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts259" ANNOTATION_ID="a3371534"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich erinnere mich gut daran, wie mir meine Mutter das erzählt und erklärt hat.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts308" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts313" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130024"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das ist eine gute Frage.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts313" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts320" ANNOTATION_ID="a3911291"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Als es passiert war/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts320" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts367" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130025"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Einen Tag nach dem es passiert war, wusste man nicht, ob es Selbstmord war oder nur ein Unfall wegen eines Fehlers am Auto.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts367" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts382" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130026"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dann war ich traurig darüber.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts382" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts394" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130028"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich konnte das nicht glauben.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts394" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts409" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677080"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wie ihr wisst, ist der Unfall ja in einem Tunnel passiert.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts409" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts429" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677082"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Es war traurig, dass es so eine wertvolle Person nicht mehr geben würde.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts429" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts440" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130031"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Und, dass sie so jung gestorben ist.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts440" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts471" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130032"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Man dachte, sie würde als Königin mit dem Mann weiterleben, aber jetzt ist sie nicht mehr unter uns.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts471" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts490" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130033"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Deshalb hat mich diese Geschichte damals bewegt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts491" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts497" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130034"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Eine gute Frage.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts497" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts540" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677159"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Also beim Unfall hat der Fahrer einen Fehler gemacht. Der Fahrer fuhr in den Tunnel.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts540" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts559" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130036"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Es war ein Autounfall, oder/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts559" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts566" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130038"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Es war Selbstmord oder/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts566" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts571" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130040"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oder Mord oder so.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts571" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts579" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130041"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Der Unfall wurde ja untersucht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts579" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts587" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130042"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Genau weiß ich es nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts587" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts612" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130055"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich hatte nur erfahren, dass Diana dabei gestorben war. Aber wie es passiert ist, davon habe ich keine Ahnung.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts612" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts621" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130060"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie sind in den Tunnel gefahren.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts621" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts642" ANNOTATION_ID="a2130063"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ob es Selbstmord oder ein Fehler des Fahrers war, weiß ich nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts721" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts733" ANNOTATION_ID="a2131903"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, durch das Fernsehen am nächsten Tag.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts733" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts738" ANNOTATION_ID="a2131911"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Es wurde überall davon berichtet.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts738" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts759" ANNOTATION_ID="a2131924"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Einen Tag, nachdem es passiert ist, habe ich es im Fernsehen gesehen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts759" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts766" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677586"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Meine Mutter meinte: „Schau mal!“</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts766" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts773" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677587"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dann guckten wir zusammen und sie war ganz traurig.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts773" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts786" ANNOTATION_ID="a2131963"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Da hat meine Mutter von dem Tod erzählt und dass sie traurig ist.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts786" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts821" ANNOTATION_ID="a2131987"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wir verfolgten die ganze Geschichte bis hin zur großen Beerdigung, die auch traurig war.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts821" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts826" ANNOTATION_ID="a2131989"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Darum.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts827" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts842" ANNOTATION_ID="a2712224"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Man denkt jedes Jahr an sie.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts842" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts849" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132000"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Denn sie war einfach was Besonderes.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts849" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts864" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132005"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Normalerweise gedenkt man besonderen Anlässen nur alle 5 oder 10 Jahre.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts864" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts881" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132011"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Aber wenn man Diana sieht, erinnert man sich an die Vergangenheit.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts886" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts891" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132037"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Nein, das war zu weit weg.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts917" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts930" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132066"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wenn der Termin passen würde, vielleicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts930" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts939" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132071"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Jedenfalls habe ich es bis jetzt immer verpasst.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts939" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts950" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132074"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ob ich jemals daran teilnehmen werde, weiß ich nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts952" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts975" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132089"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das Besondere an ihr war, dass sie für die Armen und Kinder auf der ganzen Welt da war.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts975" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts986" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132091"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie umarmte sie und kümmerte sich um sie.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts986" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1001" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132092"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Die Armen waren froh, wenn sie zu ihnen kam.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1001" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1012" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132094"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie war die Königin mit Herz für/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1012" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1026" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132096"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie hatte ein Herz für Kinder.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1026" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1039" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132098"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dafür bewunderte ich sie.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1065" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1070" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132124"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das weiß ich nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1070" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1077" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677658"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich glaube schon.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1077" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1084" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132136"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Es wäre schon alles weitergegangen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1084" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1098" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132139"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie war ja ein sehr lieber Mensch.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1098" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1104" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132143"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie hatte ein Herz für Kinder.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1104" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1109" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677661"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Da hätte sich was entwickelt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1109" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1140" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132151"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Aber ob die Welt dadurch anders geworden wäre, wie du eben sagtest, weiß ich nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1159" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1166" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132171"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Davon weiß ich nichts.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1227" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1246" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132202"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich habe keine Ahnung davon, deshalb.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1247" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1250" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132217"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Okay.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1251" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1262" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132235"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Zwei Kinder.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1262" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1272" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677671"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, die beiden sind Brüder, ein älterer und ein jüngerer.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1272" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1281" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132279"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Der eine hat vor kurzem geheiratet.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1281" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1294" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132292"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Der große Bruder ist ein verheirateter Mann.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1294" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1316" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132302"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Er hat vor Kurzem Kate geheiratet, Kate, stimmts?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1316" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1329" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132338"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie haben geheiratet, Glückwunsch.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1329" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1339" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132339"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie lieben sich.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1339" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1346" ANNOTATION_ID="a2204454"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Davor habe ich Respekt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1347" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1352" ANNOTATION_ID="a2141666"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Nein.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1378" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1396" ANNOTATION_ID="a2141999"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Hmm, also ich denke, dass er damit richtig liegt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1423" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1437" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142035"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, in London.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1437" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1448" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677688"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Es ist ja eine große Familie.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1448" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1458" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142041"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich kenne nur einige davon.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1458" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1471" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142043"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Alle kenne ich nicht, nur einige.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1471" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1493" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142047"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Zum Beispiel kenne ich Diana und die Oma.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1493" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1502" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142048"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich kenne auch nicht alle Namen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1502" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1513" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142049"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Nur von einigen bekannten Personen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1513" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1520" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142051"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Mehr nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1628" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1644" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142073"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, vor allem im Norden Europas gibt es viele Könige.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1644" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1669" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142074"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wie zum Beispiel in England, Schweden, Finnland und Norwegen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1669" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1673" ANNOTATION_ID="a2677722"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Mehr im Norden.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION></TIER><TIER TIER_ID="Translation_into_English_B" LINGUISTIC_TYPE_REF="L_text__coarser_granularity" PARTICIPANT="ber-42"><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts21" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692324"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>When I heard about Diana's fatal accident I was very sad.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts21" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts50" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692325"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>When she was alive she gave the world and the poor protection, love and support.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts50" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts69" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692326"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>She was the best and nicest queen England ever had.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts69" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts84" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692327"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Therefore, I was shocked and sad about the accident.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts84" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts97" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692331"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Because she wouldn't be here anymore.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts97" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts104" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692333"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>If/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts104" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts116" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692334"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>She's done some real nice things in her life.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts116" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts142" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692335"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>She was a great role model for me.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts193" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts217" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692358"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yeah, my mom told me a lot about her.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts217" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts230" ANNOTATION_ID="a3378834"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>She talked about her accident, as well. That‘s why I knew so much about her.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts230" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts259" ANNOTATION_ID="a3378835"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I clearly remember the moment my mother told me about it, and how she explained it to me.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts308" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts313" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692375"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>That is a good question.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts313" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts320" ANNOTATION_ID="a3911296"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>When it had happened/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts320" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts367" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692393"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>The day after it had happened, people didn't know if it was suicide or an accident due to a malfunction of the car.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts367" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts382" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692397"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Then I was sad about it all.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts382" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts394" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692398"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I couldn't believe all this.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts394" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts409" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692400"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>As you know the accident happened in a tunnel.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts409" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts429" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692408"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>It was sad that such a precious person was no longer alive.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts429" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts440" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692409"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>And that she died so young.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts440" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts471" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692416"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Everyone thought she would continue living as the queen with that man, but now she is no longer with us.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts471" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts490" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692424"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Therefore, this story moved me a lot back then.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts491" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts497" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692436"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>That is a good question.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts497" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts540" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692445"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, the driver made a mistake. He drove the car into the tunnel.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts540" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts559" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692457"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>It was a car accident or/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts559" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts566" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692460"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>It was suicide or/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts566" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts571" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692467"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Or murder or so.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts571" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts579" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692469"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They investigated the accident.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts579" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts587" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692472"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I don't really know.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts587" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts612" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692482"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I just heard about her death, but I didn't know how it happened.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts612" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts621" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692485"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They drove into the tunnel.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts621" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts642" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692491"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I don't know if it was suicide or a mistake by the driver.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts721" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts733" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692619"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, I saw it on television the next day.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts733" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts738" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692623"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They covered the topic on all channels.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts738" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts759" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692624"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I saw it on TV a day after it happened.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts759" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts766" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692625"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>My mom said, “Look!”</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts766" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts773" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692633"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>After that we watched TV together and she was very sad.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts773" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts786" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692636"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>My mom talked about death then and she became even sadder.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts786" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts821" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692638"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>We followed up on the whole topic, even until the big funeral, which was also very sad.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts821" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts826" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692639"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>That's why.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts827" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts842" ANNOTATION_ID="a2712226"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Every year one thinks of her.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts842" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts849" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692642"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Because she was something special.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts849" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts864" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692645"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Usually one remembers such occasions only at five or ten year anniversaries.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts864" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts881" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692646"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>If you see Diana, you automatically remember everything from the past.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts886" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts891" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692647"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>No, it was too far away.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts917" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts930" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692662"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>If the date fits my calendar, maybe.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts930" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts939" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692670"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Anyways, I have always missed it so far.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts939" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts950" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692754"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I don't know if I would go.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts952" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts975" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692767"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>She was special because she was there for the poor and the children around the world.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts975" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts986" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692770"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>She hugged them and cared for them.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts986" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1001" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692771"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>The poor were glad when she visited.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1001" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1012" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692777"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>She was the queen with a heart for/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1012" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1026" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692781"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>She had a heart for children.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1026" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1039" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692783"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I admire her for that.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1065" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1070" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692804"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I don't know.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1070" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1077" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692805"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I think so.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1077" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1084" ANNOTATION_ID="a2708814"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>She would have continued the work she was already doing.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1084" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1098" 