r und wie wusstest du davon, dass Diana gestorben war?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts891" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts892" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132039"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Einen Brief schreiben und dahin schicken?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts951" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts957" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132086"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Was war für dich so besonderes an ihr?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1158" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1159" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132163"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>War Diana auch für Gehörlose da?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1246" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1247" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132215"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Er hat damit recht. Später werde ich dir mehr darüber erzählen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1250" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1251" ANNOTATION_ID="a2132226"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Gut, wie viele Kinder hatte Diana?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1346" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1347" ANNOTATION_ID="a2141665"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Zurück zu Diana, was für einen Beruf hatte sie damals gelernt und damit gearbeitet, wisst ihr es?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1361" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1362" ANNOTATION_ID="a2141992"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wen hatte Diana denn geheiratet?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1391" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1401" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142001"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Charles! C-H-A-R-L-E-S.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1414" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1417" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142008"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Und die Königin von England, wisst ihr etwas über sie?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1594" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1597" ANNOTATION_ID="a2142068"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wir kennen das Königreich von England, kennt ihr auch noch andere Könige?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION></TIER><TIER TIER_ID="Translation_into_English_Mod" LINGUISTIC_TYPE_REF="L_text__coarser_granularity" PARTICIPANT="ber-mod-1"><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts151" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts157" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692346"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Is he right about Diana?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts306" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts307" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692370"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Is there anything else you would like to say about Diana?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts307" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts308" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692372"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>How did you feel when you heard about the accident?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts490" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts491" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692434"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Do you know how this accident happened?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts642" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts643" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692504"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Do you know how it happened?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts720" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts727" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692558"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>From where and how did you learn of Diana's death?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts891" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts892" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692649"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>You mean writing a letter and sending it there?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts951" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts957" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692762"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Where there things that made her really special to you?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1158" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1159" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692845"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Did Diana also care for deaf people?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1246" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1247" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692870"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>He is right. I will tell you more about it later.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1250" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1251" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692871"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Alright, how many children did Diana had?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1346" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1347" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692890"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Back to Diana: What was her job before she was married, do you know that?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1361" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1362" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692891"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Who did Diana marry?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1391" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1401" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692899"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Charles! C-H-A-R-L-E-S.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1414" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1417" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692903"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>And do you know something about the Queen of England?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1594" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1597" ANNOTATION_ID="a2692924"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>We know the British Kingdom, do you also know some other kings?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION></TIER><LINGUISTIC_TYPE LINGUISTIC_TYPE_ID="L_text__coarser_granularity" TIME_ALIGNABLE="true"/><LINGUISTIC_TYPE LINGUISTIC_TYPE_ID="L_dependent_values" TIME_ALIGNABLE="false" CONSTRAINTS="Symbolic_Association"/><LINGUISTIC_TYPE LINGUISTIC_TYPE_ID="L_tokens_right_left__finer_granularity" TIME_ALIGNABLE="true"/><LINGUISTIC_TYPE LINGUISTIC_TYPE_ID="L_text__finer_granularity" TIME_ALIGNABLE="true"/><LINGUISTIC_TYPE LINGUISTIC_TYPE_ID="L_text__mouth__standard_orthography__coarser_granularity" TIME_ALIGNABLE="true"/><CONSTRAINT STEREOTYPE="Symbolic_Association" DESCRIPTION="1-1 association with a parent annotation"/></ANNOTATION_DOCUMENT>
